    "This approach allows us to better understand and harness the collective capabilities of different agents, thereby enhancing the system's adaptability and resilience.",
    "Importantly, this perspective aligns with emerging technology paradigms that foster a deep understanding and integration of human agents.",
    "Indeed, our contribution can be seen as a systemic evolution in design approaches, emphasizing the front-end to enhance usability and effectiveness.",
